fields.name: Classifications
fields.description: The classification(s) of the patch as provided by the patch publisher.

fields.name: InstallationState
fields.description: The state of the patch after the installation operation completed.

fields.name: KbId
fields.description: The KBID of the patch. Only applies to Windows patches.

fields.name: Name
fields.description: The friendly name of the patch.

fields.name: PatchId
fields.description: A unique identifier for the patch.

fields.name: Version
fields.description: The version string of the package. It may conform to Semantic Versioning. Only applies to Linux.
